title: Penny Skateboards and Lizzie Armanto in Barcelona
description:
Penny Skateboards - http://www.pennyskateboards.com
Explore Barcelona with X Games Gold Medalist Lizzie Armanto. Along with Penny Skateboards and Mahfia TV, Lizzie checks out some of the best skate and tourist spots this beautiful Spanish city has to offer. 

Music By: Trails & Ways
